data.description: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a meticulously maintained smart home, the coveted Columbia model. This residence is ready for a new family with its generous five bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a valuable bonus loft. The open-concept floor plan features tile flooring throughout the main living areas, offering an elegant yet low-maintenance space. Plush carpeting in the bedrooms ensures a comfortable retreat for relaxation. The kitchen is the heart of the home, complete with beautiful granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Additional amenities and features are thoughtfully incorporated throughout this property, ensuring your comfort and convenience. Don't delay; seize your chance to own this smart home now. Your brighter future begins here!
